@FirinApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5220
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Health check (API + PostgreSQL durumu)
GET {{FirinApi_HostAddress}}/health

### 1) Giriş yap → token al
# @name login
POST {{FirinApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### 2) Menü (herkese açık)
GET {{FirinApi_HostAddress}}/api/breads

### 3) Ekmek ekle (token gerekli)
POST {{FirinApi_HostAddress}}/api/breads
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Simit",
  "price": 15,
  "stockQuantity": 100
}

### 4) Müşteri ekle (token gerekli)
POST {{FirinApi_HostAddress}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "fullName": "Ali Yılmaz",
  "email": "ali@example.com",
  "phone": "05551234567"
}

### 5) Sipariş oluştur (token gerekli)
POST {{FirinApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "items": [
    { "productType": 1, "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### 6) Sipariş iptal et → stok geri iade edilir
POST {{FirinApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Alternatif: durumu "İptal" (3) yaparak da iptal edebilirsiniz
PATCH {{FirinApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": 3
}
